cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite both the thesis and this repository."
title: "Replication code for: From Viewing to Doing? A Randomised Evaluation of Avatar-Led Onboarding in an AI Video Platform"
abstract: >-
  Analysis code reproducing the tables, figures, and summary statistics for a
  randomised field experiment comparing avatar-led and matched non-avatar
  onboarding in an AI video platform. Code only; the underlying telemetry is
  pseudonymised personal data under the GDPR and is not distributed.
type: software
authors:
